data.text: A <xref>fried</xref> <xref>corn</xref> or <xref>flour</xref> <xref>tortilla</xref>, filled usually with <xref>beef</xref> or <xref>chicken</xref> and <xref>cheese</xref>, rolled up, and dipped in a form of <xref>salsa</xref>, or <xref>guacamole</xref>.
